To baldroofer, I am glad you have made peace with yourself and with God. Please understand that if all Americans had felt the same in 1940, all of Europe would now be under Nazi control, and this country as well! We would not have the right or the privilege to express any of the views posted at this sight. Is it better to die young at peace with God than to kill others for the sake of a few more years on this earth? Only time will tell.
